5: Mister Alk, Mister Nimbus! I'm ready!
14:
Nice job, smooth as usual. I think
that does it for the monsters in this
area.
18:
Then perhaps we should take a
break? Using a large spell like that
must be quite taxing, Kyoka.
22:
N-no, I'm good to keep going! I want
to explore the Kaleidoscope even
more.
26:
...I can't afford to slack off. Not if I
want to find a way back home to
Landosol.
31:
I get where you're coming from, but
rushing into things never helped
anyone. You gotta know when to
rest.
38:
Still, I can't believe that even Mimi
and Misogi ended up in Palpebra!
42: I need to step up my game.
50:
The Kaleidoscope is rife with
mysteries. There will be plenty of
discoveries yet—don't be
disheartened.
58:
She seems pretty down in the
dumps.
67:
Um... If you wouldn't mind, could you
help me out again tomorrow?
72: I mean, I'm totally up for it, but—
79:
A-ah! Th-that was... You didn't hear
that!
83:
Hey, I had an idea. We could all use
a refresher right about now—how
about we have dinner at our place?
86:
You can invite Mimi and Misogi too!
What do you think?
90: I mean... I could do that, but...
96: I... I need to work harder.
105:
Oh, hello. Thank you very much for
the meal. It was delicious.
110:
No problem, I'm just happy you liked
it.
113:
...But I get the feeling it didn't help
much with your mood, huh?
117: N-no, that's not true! It did!
120:
It's just... I heard Mimi and Misogi
talking during dinner.
123:
They made new friends and went
exploring around different worlds.
131: Do you not like it when they have fun?
136: N-no! That's definitely not the case...
139:
It makes me happy seeing the two
of them laughing and smiling like
that.
147:
But... There's no time. I have to think
about finding a way back home...
150:
The Gourmet Guild members told
me that all of you have an
important mission as well.
153:
We can't expect you to take care of
us forever...
157:
I like having you and the others here,
Kyoka. It's fun.
168:
Exploring the Kaleidoscope, getting
a chance to see all sorts of different
worlds... It's so exciting!
176:
Then... I guess it might be okay... to
just have fun?
185:
W-wait a minute... What are you two
doing?!
195:
Good morning. Feeling chipper
today or what?
199:
Very. Thanks to our talk yesterday, I
think I've managed to get my
thoughts all in order.
204:
All right, so are we heading off to the
Kaleidoscope or what?
211:
I was hoping that today... We could
go visit a different world!
219:
Of course! Let's do it! Got any
requests?
223:
I don't know where to begin, so...
Anywhere is fine!
229:
Then let's go see many different
places.
